therian.position.relative

Class Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • therian.position.relative.Element

  • public class Element
extends Object
    Provides fluent access to RelativePositionFactory instances for:
    • array elements
    • List elements
    • Iterable elements (requires IterableELResolver)
    Because this implementation uses unified EL facilities, growing lists/collections is not supported.
